<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٥٥ سورة الرحمن]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة الرحمن <span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٨]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>الرَّحْمنُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> عَلَّمَ الْقُرْآنَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> خَلَقَ الْإِنْسانَ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> عَلَّمَهُ الْبَيانَ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>الشَّمْسُ وَالْقَمَرُ بِحُسْبانٍ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> وَالنَّجْمُ وَالشَّجَرُ يَسْجُدانِ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وَالسَّماءَ رَفَعَها وَوَضَعَ الْمِيزانَ <span class="c2">(٧)</span> أَلاَّ تَطْغَوْا فِي الْمِيزانِ <span class="c2">(٨)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١-<span class="c5"> الرَّحْمنُ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>من أسمائه تعالى.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> عَلَّمَ الْقُرْآنَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَلَّمَ الإنسان القرآن ويسره له.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> خَلَقَ الْإِنْسانَ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أوجده.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٤-<span class="c5"> عَلَّمَهُ الْبَيانَ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>علمه الإبانة عما فى نفسه بالكلام.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٥-<span class="c5"> الشَّمْسُ وَالْقَمَرُ بِحُسْبانٍ:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>بِحُسْبانٍ يجريان بحساب وتقدير.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٦-<span class="c5"> وَالنَّجْمُ وَالشَّجَرُ يَسْجُدانِ:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَالنَّجْمُ والنبات الذي لا ساق له.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَالشَّجَرُ الذي يقوم على ساق.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>يَسْجُدانِ يخضعان لله تعالى فى كل ما يريد بهما.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٧-<span class="c5"> وَالسَّماءَ رَفَعَها وَوَضَعَ الْمِيزانَ:</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>رَفَعَها خلقها مرفوعة.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>وَوَضَعَ الْمِيزانَ وشرع العدل.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٨-<span class="c5"> أَلَّا تَطْغَوْا فِي الْمِيزانِ:</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>